0:00:00.000,0:00:06.320
Mwoyo wako ikamuri ya Mwari, kwete kamuri yekutandarira.

0:00:06.320,0:00:20.360
"Mwoyo wako ikamuri ya Mwari" zvinoreva kuti "Mwoyo wako ikamuri ye kunamatira", kwete kamuri ye kutandarira.

0:00:20.360,0:00:30.120
"Mwoyo wako ikamuri ya Mwari" zvinoreva kuti "ikamuri ya Mwari yekunyengeterera".

0:00:30.120,0:00:33.100
Uri kuitei nemwoyo wako?

0:00:33.100,0:00:38.180
Wakakangamwira avo vakakutadzira here?

0:00:38.180,0:00:41.080
Chii chawakachengeta?

0:00:41.080,0:00:55.140
Mwoyo wako uri mujeri - marwadzo ekare, godo ne shanje here?

0:00:55.140,0:01:09.440
Kana mwoyo wako usina kusununguka, hamuna nzvimbo ya Mwari nokuti mwoyo wako ikamuri ya Mwari.

0:01:09.440,0:01:15.120
Iwe une mukana, nyasha ikozvino tisati tatanga kunyengetera.

0:01:15.120,0:01:17.940
Iwe unogona kutanga kuyananisa zvino.

0:01:17.940,0:01:26.880
Zviudze kuti, "Ndinorevesa".

0:01:26.880,0:01:41.400
Ungave wagona kana kuti watadza - mumwe munhu akakutadzira - iwe hauna kodzero yekuchengeta chigumbu.

0:01:41.400,0:01:51.660
Kana iwe uchichengeta chigumbu kune hama yako, iwe watotanga kushungurudza Mweya Mutsvene.

0:01:51.660,0:01:56.520
Chigumbu kune hama yako - hazvinei kuti wagona.....

0:01:56.520,0:02:04.800
Iwe wakanyengerwa nemaune nekuda kwechikonzero chinozivikanwa newe ...

0:02:04.800,0:02:13.440
Vatariri pasi pose, hatigone kunyengetera kana tisina Mweya Mutsvene.

0:02:13.440,0:02:17.300
Iwe unofanirwa kuziva kuti iwe uriwaani tisati tanyengetera.

0:02:17.300,0:02:18.700
Ndiri waani?

0:02:18.700,0:02:22.020
Ndinoziva kuti ndiri waani.

0:02:22.020,0:02:32.640
Ini ndiri wehuvepo hwa Mwari nokuti muhuvepo Hwake, iwe une simba, unogutsikana, unofadzwa.

0:02:32.640,0:02:35.200
Gungano Rekunze

0:02:35.200,0:02:38.560
Svondo Yemusi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:02:38.560,0:02:45.020
Izvozvi, tanga kuzviyananisa pachako.

0:02:45.020,0:02:52.960
Tanga kuregerera ne kukanganwa.

0:02:52.960,0:02:57.340
Ndiregerere ini sekuregerera kwandinoita avo vanonditadzira ini.

0:02:57.340,0:02:59.940
Muzita ra Jesu Kristu, tinonamata.

0:02:59.940,0:03:02.480
(Ameni.)

0:03:02.480,0:03:06.200
Iwe unofanirwa kurevesa.

0:03:06.200,0:03:18.640
Iwe unofanirwa kubvumira mwoyo wako kuti utaure nokuti chinhu chaicho pauri mwoyo wako.

0:03:18.640,0:03:21.480
Mweya wako, mwoyo wako ndiwo chinhu chaicho.

0:03:21.480,0:03:22.980
Rega mwoyo wako utaure.

0:03:22.980,0:03:25.040
Revesa ne mwoyo wako wese.

0:03:25.040,0:03:26.940
Nezita ra Jesu, tinonamata.

0:03:26.940,0:03:28.860
(Ameni.)

0:03:28.860,0:03:32.100
Svondo Yemusi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:03:32.100,0:03:41.760
Avo vedu avo vachiri kurwisana nezvekare zvedu, marwadzo ekare, mhosva dzenguva yakapfuura,

0:03:41.760,0:03:46.060
Ndinonamata kuti unosunungurwa, nezita ra Jesu.

0:03:46.060,0:03:48.860
(Ameni!)

0:03:48.860,0:03:50.540
Sunungurwa, nezita ra Jesu.

0:03:50.540,0:03:53.620
(Ameni!)

0:03:53.620,0:04:00.020
Iwe hausi pano kuzosangana nemunhu asi iwe uri pano kuzosangana na Mwari.

0:04:00.020,0:04:04.100
Mwari haasi munhu.

0:04:04.100,0:04:06.560
Muzita ra Jesu, iwe wasunungurwa.

0:04:06.560,0:04:08.600
(Ameni.)

0:04:08.600,0:04:10.440
Sunungurwa, nezita ra Jesu.

0:04:10.440,0:04:14.120
(Ameni.)

0:04:14.120,0:04:16.900
Kubva pakurwadziwa kwekare, sunungurwa muzita ra Jesu.

0:04:16.900,0:04:21.380
(Ameni.)

0:04:21.380,0:04:23.800
Kubva pa pfini idzodzo, sunungurwa, nezita ra Jesu.

0:04:23.800,0:04:28.720
(Ameni.)

0:04:28.720,0:04:35.680
Kubva pakutsamwa uku, sunungurwa, nezita ra Jesu.

0:04:35.680,0:04:47.820
Vatariri, ndinoisa ruoko rwangu pamusoro penyu, kukusunungurai kubva pakurwadziwa kwekare uku.

0:04:47.820,0:04:49.520
(Ameni!)

0:04:49.520,0:04:51.520
Ndinoisa ruoko rwangu pamusoro pako.

0:04:51.520,0:04:54.560
Sunungurwa, muzita ra Jesu! (Ameni!)

0:04:54.560,0:05:00.700
Marwadzo ekare, sunungurwa, muzita ra Jesu! (Ameni!)

0:05:00.700,0:05:03.700
Gamuchira hunhu hwa Mwari, muzita ra Jesu.

0:05:03.700,0:05:08.320
(Ameni!)

0:05:08.320,0:05:11.900
Muzita ra Jesu Kristu. (Ameni!)

0:05:11.900,0:05:14.160
Ameni. (Ameni.)

0:05:14.160,0:05:17.640
Ndinoda kutenda kuti wasunungurwa.

0:05:17.640,0:05:22.440
Uchatenda pamwe neni here?

0:05:22.440,0:05:25.400
Garai henyu pasi.

0:05:25.400,0:05:37.360
Sezvo iwe uchitenda pamwe neni - vatendi vaviri vari nani kupfuura umwe, kana vari pamwechete.

0:05:37.360,0:05:42.960
Sezvo iwe uchitenda pamwe neni kuti iwe wasunungurwa, iwe wasunungurwa.

0:05:42.960,0:05:44.620
(Ameni.)

0:05:44.620,0:05:48.240
Zvino, iwe unogona kunzwa huvepo hwa Mwari.

0:05:48.240,0:05:49.640
(Ameni.)

0:05:49.640,0:05:51.620
Uri kunzwa here huvepo hwa Mwari?

0:05:51.620,0:05:53.120
(Hongu)

0:05:53.120,0:05:58.400
Inguva yako yekusangana na Ishe.

0:05:58.400,0:06:03.780
Svondo Yemusi We Svondo Pa SCOAN

0:06:03.780,0:06:06.020
Hareruya.

0:06:06.020,0:06:12.460
Apo tirikufambira mberi, Mweya unosunungura shoko Rake.

0:06:12.460,0:06:19.660
Aya ndiwo mazwi ekutenda achakuvaka iwe, kwete mazano chete.

0:06:19.660,0:06:21.900
Hareruya.(Ameni)

0:06:21.900,0:06:29.280
Kana tichiti, "Ndiri munhu anotenda", vazhinji vedu hatizivi zvazvinoreva.

0:06:29.280,0:06:33.220
Tinongonzwa vanhu vachiti, "Ndiri murume wekutenda, ini ndiri mukadzi anotenda."

0:06:33.220,0:06:39.200
Zvinorevei kwauri kana uchiti, "Ndiri munhu anotenda; Ndiri mukadzi anotenda "?

0:06:39.200,0:06:43.680
Ndiro zita redu sevaKristu - "Ndiri munhu wekutenda."

0:06:43.680,0:06:49.240
Iwe haufaniri kuzviti "mukadzi anotenda" asi iwe usingazivi zvazvinoreva.

0:06:49.240,0:06:53.060
Zvinoreva kuti ndinovimba na Mwari nerutendo rwangu rwose.

0:06:53.060,0:06:56.200
Ndiri "mukadzi anotenda" ... - madzimai, umwe munhu angataura pano here?

0:06:56.200,0:07:00.780
Kutenda mune Shoko ra Mwari ... nekurarama sezvinotaurwa neShoko ra Mwari

0:07:00.780,0:07:10.340
Kana tichiti, "Ndiri munhu anotenda", zvinoreva kuti iwe unoshandisa mazwi ekutenda ne kubereka zvibereko zvekutenda.

0:07:10.340,0:07:11.360
Ndizvozvo.

0:07:11.360,0:07:13.960
Iwe unoshandisa mazwi ekutenda.

0:07:13.960,0:07:16.900
Unoziva here zvazvinoreva kushandisa mazwi ekutenda?

0:07:16.900,0:07:23.640
Kana ndichiti ndiri munhu anotenda, ndiri kushandisa mazwi ekutenda kuti ndive nemigumisiro yekutenda.

0:07:23.640,0:07:29.360
Kana asingabereke zvibereko zvekutenda, zvinoreva kuti kutenda kwangu rutendo mukutenda,

0:07:29.360,0:07:33.080
kwete kutenda mumabasa akapedzwa aIshe wedu Jesu Kristu.

0:07:33.080,0:07:36.640
Ndinorevei kana ndichiti mutauro we Bhaibheri?

0:07:36.640,0:07:49.960
Ndiyo mutauro uyo Mwari akashandiswa kutisika ne kutiponesa, kuti poresa, kuti ropafadza kuti tonga, ne kutiraira.

0:07:49.960,0:07:52.700
Uyu ndiwo mutauro we Bhaibheri.

0:07:52.700,0:08:01.180
Mutauro wenhasi ndiwo mutauro watinoshandisa nguva dzose kunze uko, kutaura makuhwa, kupa mirairidzo,

0:08:01.180,0:08:05.500
"Ita izvi! Unogona kuita izvi!" - hauna hanya nezvaunotaura;

0:08:05.500,0:08:10.460
kana kutaura nevana vako, "Ndapota, iwe uri benzi. Uya pano",

0:08:10.460,0:08:18.060
kana kuimba nziyo - chero ani zvake anogona kuimba nziyo, kunyange nziyo dzevhangeri, kunyange asiri mu Kristu,

0:08:18.060,0:08:21.880
kuti utaure nyaya - ndiwo mutauro wanhasi,

0:08:21.880,0:08:30.100
kuti uite bhizinesi - munoziva mabhizinesi anhasi une makadhi ebhizinesi enhema - nhau, kureva nhema,

0:08:30.100,0:08:33.720
kuita zvematongerwo enyika nhasi.

0:08:33.720,0:08:36.000
Ndiwo mutauro wanhasi.

0:08:36.000,0:08:39.740
Paunenge uchiti, "Ndiri murume wekutenda" kana kuti "Ndiri mukadzi anotenda",

0:08:39.740,0:08:46.040
zvinoreva kuti iwe unoshandisa mazwi ekutenda nekubereka zvibereko zvekutenda.

